# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manage KubeVirt data volumes attached to virtual machines in Spectro Cloud.

## Example Usage

```hcl
resource "spectrocloud_datavolume" "example" {
  cluster_context = "project"
  cluster_uid     = "cluster-uid"
  vm_name         = "vm-example"
  vm_namespace    = "default"

  metadata {
    name      = "data-volume-example"
    namespace = "default"
  }

  # Full spec omitted for brevity.
  spec {}

  add_volume_options {
    name = "data-volume-example"

    disk {
      name = "data-volume-example"
      bus  = "virtio"
    }

    volume_source {
      data_volume {
        name         = "data-volume-example"
        hotpluggable = true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

